<div style="line-height: 24px; text-align: center; max-width: 32rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid rgb(75 85 99/1); margin: 2.5rem; padding: 2.5rem">
  <h2>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</h2>

  <p>Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>

  <p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), style: 'border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 10px 25px; color: white; background: rgb(108 43 217/1); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;' %></p>

  <p style="color: #c65029;">If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
  <p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
</div>
